hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180503/photo/bkn-20180503175529719-0503_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180503190325\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180503%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180503175529719-0503_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180503190325&h=24e4cb3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女子持刀危坐酒店簷蓬！今午5時許，一名女子攀上油麻地彌敦道近永星里一間酒店的簷篷，掛上一幅約6呎乘10呎橫額，手持鎅刀危坐，途人見狀報警。消防員接報到場，在彌敦道南行線張開救生氣墊戒備，又派「飛將軍」在酒店一、二樓留意情況。期間，女事主不停在簷篷來回踱步，又在邊緣位置危坐，警方談判專家到場展開游說。 <br />\n<br />\n女子掛起的橫額，則以簡體字寫上「山高皇帝遠，孤兒寡婦上訪十年申訴無門，香港同胞我對不起你們」，事件引來大批市民圍觀。事件導致彌敦道南行近永星里往尖沙咀方向兩條行車線封閉，交通十分擠塞。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T11:22:53.000Z","msg":"同你老母胞<br />\n喺度認親認戚<br />\n支那閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2755675b54996a729344c25885f756a79ae1b275","tid":651733,"uid":65123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9112026f2b178966db5e21acca83f9031e4d804","tid":651733,"uid":48500,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T10:59:25.000Z","msg":"人地平台坐一坐喊兩聲聽日就有社處跟進上公屋,港豬比佢攪到返唔到屋企聽日又返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T11:23:12.000Z","msg":"心水清巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一樓跳樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係要死嘅 就上高啲樓層先跳"},{"pid":"d6f6fa5664d10817eb16fe4b06d20bd72992c879","tid":651733,"uid":156345,"like":79,"dislike":1,"score":78,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T11:23:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/03/192335_1ffa23ea7352cbed5a5e1a3de3faede0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F20